{
  "stem": "24651.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came on a visitor's visa, which allowed us to be in the United States for 90 days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that point, you know, the only way we could remain if-- was if my father married an American.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the family kind of searched and looked for a single, eligible woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they found my stepmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We came in March, and they were married in June.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] And when we first came, we lived with my uncle and my aunt.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Rahway, New Jersey.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and my uncle and my-- he married an American woman-- my aunt Rose-- and her brother and sister, and we lived with them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My uncle took me-- so this was end of March.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, actually, though, April, because by the time we arrived-- and like-- like toward-- I think in May-- they took me-- my uncle took me to school to enroll me in school.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- well, before that-- before that, there was this real attempt to make me an American child, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no assimilate-- there was assimilation rather than maintaining your own, you know, identity.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so my hair was cut-- cut short.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, like my aunt took me for clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and-- Did-- did you want to be more American?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you remember?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember wanting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was a child who was just so complacent, because I just did what I was told to do.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like-- I don't remember rebelling, or wanting, or not wanting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was like, look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is what needs to happen, and it happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think it was just so deeply ingrained that my-- my life depended on it, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
